articles.title: Record breakers: South Africa make more history at Cricket World Cup - ICC Women's World Cup
articles.description: A rampant South Africa continue to shatter records with their big-hitting and huge totals, but the Proteas’ attack has also set new benchmarks during an imperious run at the ICC Men’s Cricket World Cup.
